      "content": "sometimes i just sit here in this cafe and watch people walk by and it hits me how much of a non-entity i am. like i'm just a ghost in a different time zone. if i just stopped existing tomorrow, the world wouldn't even flicker. it's like i'm a zero-sum person. i take up space but i don't actually add anything.",
